additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Corrosive to eyes when undiluted. Avoid contact of undiluted product with eyes and skin. Dispose of empty container with household recycling. Not to be taken. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (phone Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If swallowed, do NOT induce vomiting. If in eyes, hold eyelids apart and flush eye continuously with running water. Continue to flush until advised to stop by the poisons information centre or a doctor, or for at least 15 minutes. If undiluted product is on skin, wash thoroughly.
